description: Today I went to a sports park. It was a pretty sweet idea because the place was full of young guys. My first stop was a skateboard place. It took me less than a minute to find a perfect pair of dudes. I should try these spots more often. The boys were good friends, who knew each other for years. They decided to brush up on their skateboarding skills and I interrupted them. Luckily, they were okay with a little chat. Both boys were students and both had crappy part-time jobs. No surprise that my money caught their attention. I couldn´t believe that these innocent looking angels could be so greedy. Every proposition I gave them was countered with a simple question: "how much"? They both had girlfriends but none of them seemed to have any remorse after fulfilling my every dirty wish.
title: Czech Hunter 375
